title: Schedule of Judge Sotomayor's Capitol Hill meetings today, 6-17-09 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




June 17, 2009

 



Schedule of Judge Sotomayor's Capitol Hill meetings today, 6-17-09




 THE WHITE HOUSE Office of the Press Secretary  ________________________________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                                                     June 17, 2009    SCHEDULE OF JUDGE SOTOMAYOR’S CAPITOL HILL MEETINGS  WEDNESDAY, JUNE 17  Today, Judge Sotomayor will visit Capitol Hill to meet with the following Senators: Senator Lamar Alexander  Senator Bob Bennett  Senator Saxby Chambliss  Senator Chris Dodd  Senator Byron Dorgan  Senator Jim Webb
